articles.author: CBS News
articles.title: American missionaries killed by gang in Haiti - CBS News
articles.description: A young American couple doing missionary work in Haiti was killed in a gang ambush, according to their family. Now the White House is raising the pressure for an international force to take control of Haiti's security. Manuel Bojorquez has the latest.
